> aitchison_distance = dist(clr_data, method=?euclidean?)
> pca_data = dudi.pca(data.frame(aitchison_distance))
>
> Cheers
> Johannes
>
> > On 22 Feb 2022, at 05:11, Terri Lacourse <tlacours at uvic.ca> wrote:
